# Documenting analytics and tagging changes

Any change to **tagging**, **event names**, **event properties**, **when events fire**, or other **analytics** behavior **must** update **`docs/events.md`** in the same change (funnel mapping, event catalog, property notes, and naming conventions if the contract changes).

Do not merge analytics-only code changes without the matching documentation update. When events are registered or described in PostHog, keep the **live project** (definitions, tags) consistent with `docs/events.md` as part of the same release when practical.
